<paragraph blockId="7.[189,1399,267,366]" pageId="7" pageNumber="8">
According to these new nomenclatural arrangements, it is noteworthy to reconsider the name of the species group to which 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Billberg" authorityYear="1815" box="[475,585,303,330]" class="Insecta" family="Scarabaeidae" genus="Onthophagus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="7" pageNumber="8" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="hircus">
<emphasis box="[475,585,303,330]" italics="true" pageId="7" pageNumber="8">O. hircus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
belongs. Therefore, the 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Mannerheim" authorityYear="1829" box="[881,976,303,329]" class="Insecta" family="Scarabaeidae" genus="Onthophagus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="7" pageNumber="8" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="hirculus">
<emphasis box="[881,976,303,329]" italics="true" pageId="7" pageNumber="8">hirculus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
group, as originally established by 
<bibRefCitation author="Zunino M. &amp; Halffter G." box="[189,492,339,365]" journalOrPublisher="Elytron" pageId="7" pageNumber="8" pagination="157 - 178" part="11" refId="ref11176" refString="Zunino M. &amp; Halffter G. 1997. Sobre Onthophagus Latreille, 1802 Americanos (Coleoptera: Scarabaeidae: Scarabaeinae). Elytron 11: 157 - 178." title="Sobre Onthophagus Latreille, 1802 Americanos (Coleoptera: Scarabaeidae: Scarabaeinae)" type="journal article" year="1997">Zunino &amp; Halffter (1997)</bibRefCitation>
, is here renamed the 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Billberg" authorityYear="1815" box="[740,812,339,365]" class="Insecta" family="Scarabaeidae" genus="Onthophagus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="7" pageNumber="8" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="hircus">
<emphasis box="[740,812,339,365]" italics="true" pageId="7" pageNumber="8">hircus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
group.
</paragraph>
